    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1936-11-19T10:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1936-11-19T10:00:00-05:00" n="806"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d806">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">852.00/3795: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Consul at Seville</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Bay</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1936-11-19T10:00:00-05:00"
                            >November 19, 1936—10 a.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Although the Embassy quarter in Madrid has not so far been subjected to
                    bombardment we are informed that the British Foreign Office has instructed its
                    Ambassador at Hendaye as a precautionary measure informally to request the
                    Burgos Junta to extend the Madrid safety zone sufficiently far to the west of
                    Castellana Avenue to include the British, American and other nearby Embassies
                    and Legations.</p>
                <p>Please request General Queipo de Llano to inform General Franco <pb facs="0863"
                        n="764" xml:id="pg_764"/> that we associate ourselves unreservedly with this
                    British request and earnestly hope that he will comply therewith to the fullest
                    extent within his power.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Moore</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
